The paper proposes a framework for transparent reporting of machine learning models, with a focus on human-centered models in computer vision and natural language processing. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV), and Cybernetics (cs.CY).
